{"tid":553553,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【流感肆虐】多區大爆發！4校85人感染 兩童併發腦病變","createTime":"2018-02-07T14:36:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-07T15:11:49.000Z","uid":65346,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"52aaa349b5eb78ebf6bd447d9905f8449d52c90b","tid":553553,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T14:36:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n陷家剷 !<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180207/57804910\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180207%2F57804910&d=voCK8FXwRRmMHUQ%2Fw2iICCwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=538aaa8c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180207%2F57804910&h=a220184c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180207/57804910</a><br />\n<br />\n本港乙型流感大爆發，再有多間學校出現學童集體感染！其中一名居於荃灣的5歲女童周二（6日）發病，被送入仁濟醫院急症室，今早再轉送瑪嘉烈醫院兒科深切治療部。化驗結果顯示，女童患乙型流感併發腦病變，目前情況嚴重。而女童就讀的馬頭圍培道小學幼稚園部亦證實爆發乙型流感，該校另有5名年齡介乎4至6歲的學生出現流感樣疾病病徵，其中一人的呼吸道樣本對乙流呈陽性反應。<br />\n<br />\n到傍晚，衞生防護中心公佈另一宗兒童嚴重流感個案，患者是一名長居於北京的兩歲香港男童。中心指，該名男童於2月2日起出現發燒、咳嗽和流鼻水等病徵，翌日起更出現行為異常，5日起出現身體抽搐，至昨日（6日）被家人帶回香港到瑪麗醫院求醫，臨床診斷為乙流併發腦病變，暫時情況穩定。<br />\n另外，全港再多三間小學及一間幼稚園爆發乙流或流感樣的個案。其中元朗基督教宣道會徐澤林紀念小學、屯門順德聯誼總會何日東小學及沙田啟思幼稚園（帝堡城）有學生集體感染乙流，共有64名學生及一名女職員染病，當中大部份人都曾經求醫，其中3人要入院治療，目前仍有一人留醫。<br />\n葵涌聖公會主愛小學則爆發流感樣疾病個案，受影響班級小二、三、四、六，涉及20名學童，包括10男10女，介乎7至11歲。他們自1月21日起先後出現發燒、咳嗽、流鼻水和喉嚨痛等病徵。當中19人曾求醫，無須入院，所有人情況穩定。<br />\n中心表示，已派人到所有爆發流感的學校視察，並安排學校接受醫學監察，呼籲市民應注意良好個人和環境衞生。"},{"pid":"b3c6fc5e5bb3e901ebbb5ee28560d8b09145e225","tid":553553,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T14:41:54.000Z","msg":"衛生署, 醫管局正仆街, 又害d香港人"},{"pid":"6f48a07100d45f14415ecd8dd18e55951ec7db65","tid":553553,"uid":6869,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T14:45:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1f7a0dd3bf4458a9ca747214eef61a86e61b0535","tid":553553,"uid":8858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T14:50:50.000Z","msg":"長居北京的香港男童<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7ca8b99b01fad40a5eaf4118b989a73ef1f2972","tid":553553,"uid":104658,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T14:51:44.000Z","msg":"樓價應該好快跌  買得樓"},{"pid":"3242031bfa67b7f091103b93b6e2422329e56f9f","tid":553553,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1f7a0dd3bf4458a9ca747214eef61a86e61b0535","tid":553553,"uid":8858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T14:50:50.000Z","msg":"長居北京的香港男童<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T14:51:57.000Z","msg":"2003 沙士都係由大陸入"},{"pid":"82ca316a92092a1e0c81382d5b3896e378f3b88f","tid":553553,"uid":8858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3242031bfa67b7f091103b93b6e2422329e56f9f","tid":553553,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1f7a0dd3bf4458a9ca747214eef61a86e61b0535","tid":553553,"uid":8858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T14:50:50.000Z","msg":"長居北京的香港男童<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T14:51:57.000Z","msg":"2003 沙士都係由大陸入"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T14:55:12.000Z","msg":"仆街長居北京唔喺支那醫，返嚟香港醫<br />\n想再嚟沙士"},{"pid":"91f2ebb2b4c31b1c366194dc010acf070bbc6987","tid":553553,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"82ca316a92092a1e0c81382d5b3896e378f